25 ðær ic ær cwæð: “Ðær man wel geþeoð”,
26 and ðær ic cwæð: “Ne wearð his gelica acenned”;
27 and her is neod ðæt man wel todæle.

37 Se wæs eal seraphinisc on his mode;
38 se ðurh wisdom on eorðan wæs
39 scinende beorhtnes cherubines leohtes.

55 Nis ðæt feor ðanon ðæt eastryne,
56 ðæt he ða ongan ða eorðan feolan
57 his miclan mægenþrymmes sumne;

61 ne ontyneð duru willan ond wynna;
62 and beforan his gastlican gewitnesse
63 and coram patre he him gefæstnode;

64 Þeos, benumen hire æroran were,
65 þusend wintra and ma þæs morðre and þæs myrcan
66 oð þisne secg wunode butan gesiðum;

67 ne mihte ða gehyran ðæt he hire hold wære
68 mid Amiclate, ðurh his stefne strengð,
69 se ðe ealne ymbhwyrft egesan geworhte;

76 Hiora sib and hiora blide hleor,
77 lufu and wundor and swete gesihð,
78 worhte ðæt hi wæron gesælda gesceafta;

88 Ne him ne gewehte modgeþohtes wlite
89 forðæmðe he wæs sunu Petres Bernardones,
90 ne forðæmðe he wæs ðæs folces spotte;

112 his gebroðrum, swa swa rihtwisum yrfenumam,
113 his leofostan wif bebead,
114 and bebead ðæt hi ða lufiendan lufedon mid treowe;

118 Þence nu hwæt se wæs, se ðe weorðe wæs
119 gefēra wæs to gehealdenne ðone bát
120 Petres on ðære sæ be rihtre tacne;

121 and se wæs ūre eald fæder;
122 for ðon se ðe him æfter fylgð, swa he him tæhte,
123 ðu miht tocnawan ðæt he gōde ceape lædeð.

124 Ac his heord, mid niwum bigleofan,
125 is geworden glæm, swa ðæt beon ne mæg
126 ðæt he for mislicum stigum ne sprynge;
